org.openpnp.model

Class PlacementsHolderLocation<T extends PlacementsHolderLocation<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openpnp.model.AbstractModelObject
      • org.openpnp.model.Abstract2DLocatable<T>
        • org.openpnp.model.PlacementsHolderLocation<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.util.EventListener, Identifiable, Definable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoardLocation, PanelLocation

    public abstract class PlacementsHolderLocation<T extends PlacementsHolderLocation<T>>
extends Abstract2DLocatable<T>
    A PlacementsHolderLocation is an abstraction of a container for a subtype of a PlacementsHolder that specifies its position, orientation, and how its local coordinates transform with respect to its parent.
